   - `noHo_S`: The sequence `S` satisfies "noHo" (no one hears their own secret before each call).
   - `initPart`, `midPart`, `finalPart`: Partitions of `S` based on whether a call is "initial", "not initial and not final", or "final" (for either agent in the call).
   - `this✝`: The length of `S` is the sum of the lengths of its partitions.
